    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 naturally aspirated inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip rear differential. The chassis remains taut with documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed VANOS system, ensuring optimal variable valve timing. The vehicle exhibits excellent mechanical compression and direct steering rack feedback, making it an ideal candidate for spirited driving and long-term ownership.",
