      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a reliable daily driver and a well-cared-for enthusiast machine. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, accented by a few honest stone chips on the front bumper that testify to its road-going history. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free cabin with supple leather upholstery showing only light, natural creasing. Every electronic feature, from the climate control to the infotainment system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has been treated to consistent synthetic oil changes and recent brake service, ensuring it starts eagerly and shifts smoothly under all conditions. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. This is a thoroughly sorted, dependable car for someone who values quality and transparency.",
