      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power unit utilizes eight individual throttle bodies to deliver 414 hp with a razor-sharp 8,400 RPM redline. Power is sent through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. Recent service includes preventative rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, addressing the platform's primary mechanical concerns. The chassis remains tight, benefitting from Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and refreshed bushings. While showing minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust and the power delivery is exceptionally linear. A true driver\u2019s spec for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
